review.reviewBody: I order from here all the time and it's always fresh and delicious. Very generous portions and their fries are a little breaded so they're soft inside with a nice crisp on the outside!
I've been ordering from here for years now and the food is always hot, delicious, and the staff is so so kind!! Love this place, 10/10 ðŸ’–
Not oily, salt was just right, and the chicken to rice ratio was generous. Great value for money.
lg hashbrown add on is supposed to come with onions and peppers as per menu option.  twice I've ordered and this is what I got both times. very poor for $12.95
The chinese good combo for 2 was very good.
